title: Joey Small Hands
description: The KAJ starts with a voicemail about their negative spirit animals (00:19). Then, they dive into the big news: An Extra NFL Playoff Game (19:37), Combine Measurements (28:53), and XFL week 3 which proved no one knows anything (33:53). Later, Katie watched Wilder vs. Fury (46:50), The Emergency Back-Up Goalie (1:00:13), and BIG Bachelor Update (1:11:59). Finally, Madison Bumgarner's Alter-Ego (1:33:08) and (another) soccer coach who's mad about sex (1:36:28).
